Title: Airplane Showdown
Writer: Keegan-Michael Key (creator), Jordan Peele (creator), Rebecca Drysdale, Colton Dunn, Phil Augusta Jackson, Jay Martel, Ian Roberts, Alex Rubens, Charlie Sanders, Rich Talarico
Actors: Keegan-Michael Key, Jordan Peele, Carson Bolde, Larry Joe Campbell
Plot: A flight attendant deals with a passenger who won't fasten his seatbelt, British explorers discuss their travels, two couples try to avoid spoilers on a double date, and a prayer group receives divine intervention.
